              <h3 class="mb-3">Warrior Background of Nagaland People</h3>
        
              <p class="card-text mb-auto">Tribe traditions and loyalties play an important role in Naga society. They have a strong warrior background; they used to make armed raids to the nearby villages. Once a prevalent ritual, Head Hunting has now become obsolete. </p>
             
